  • Classes in org.alljoyn.onboarding.transport used by org.alljoyn.onboarding.transport 
    Class and Description
    ConnectionResult
    Wraps the signal that is emitted when the connection attempt against the personal AP is completed.
    ConnectionResult.ConnectionResponseType
    These enumeration values are returned from a device that supports fast channel switching .It is reported after the device tries to verify the validity of the Wi-Fi parameters received via OnboardingTransport.ConfigureWiFi(String, String, short)
    ConnectionResultAJ
    Used for passing ConnectionResult signal over the AllJoyn bus.
